Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.70,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:41.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.72,sign,,0,0,0,,Yakisoba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:46.29,sign,,0,0,0,,Hamabi Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.14,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:04.53,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:07.14,sign,,0,0,0,,Morita Technology Research Office
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.14,clover,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:09.58,clover,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:13.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.72,clover,,0,0,0,,What? Isn't he in his office?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:23.05,clover,,0,0,0,,He was singing real loud a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:25.28,clover,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:26.64,clover,,0,0,0,,But the president...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:30.79,clover,,0,0,0,,"Have this done by eight. Otherwise, you're doing ten laps around the grounds."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:31.81,clover,,0,0,0,,...said something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:34.56,clover,,0,0,0,,The president already went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:35.88,clover,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the presentation for our new project!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:41.82,clover,,0,0,0,,But he ran out screaming, "We're having curry tonight!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:44.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Curry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:53.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped if it's curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:02.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Now, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:18.63,clover,,0,0,0,,When you shine a light on it, it heads toward the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.91,clover,,0,0,0,,It's the smallest robot in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.24,clover,,0,0,0,,It's name is "kabu-tan".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Kabu-tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.23,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Kaoru's "Ka" and Shinobu's "Bu".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.18,clover,,0,0,0,,That's why it's called "Kabu-tan".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:37.00,clover,,0,0,0,,It's lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.59,clover,,0,0,0,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.00,clover,,0,0,0,,But isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.85,clover,,0,0,0,,For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:46.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Okay, why don't we have some curry then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.83,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I want some curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:28.51,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I tried to make something huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.25,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and I learned for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:36.61,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...that to build something huge, I need to make an even bigger base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:44.26,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And that the work is simple, boring and endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.57,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:56.53,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Everyone is amazed when I tell them I rode a bike to Wakkanai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:56.53,note,,0,0,0,,[ Wakkanai is the northernmost end of Japan. ]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.86,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...but all I did was pedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.21,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Right, left, right, left...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.58,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Only, endlessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:15.47,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I know that, so I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.49,thoughts,,0,0,0,,So smooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.37,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's like the edges will melt away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's like they're made out of cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.67,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The white marble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much it costs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.52,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wonder how you carve them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.08,thoughts,,0,0,0,,There's so much I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:59.61,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm brimming with thoughts of things I want to create.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:11.78,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I chase after every image that flies out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:16.22,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I catch them... I battle them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.81,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and consume them after sampling each flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:26.50,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I name and return them to where they ought to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.42,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:34.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It requires so much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.64,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I want to open all these boxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:58.02,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...but a mortal life span is too short to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:11.32,thoughts,,0,0,0,,A single lifetime limits how many boxes you can open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:16.45,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But if I had someone to help me in my battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.58,thoughts,,0,0,0,,If I have that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.79,clover,,0,0,0,,"The Gates of Hell" by Rodin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.27,clover,,0,0,0,,It's displayed at the National Museum of Western Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:29.35,clover,,0,0,0,,It appears in Dante's Divine Comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.15,clover,,0,0,0,,It's the place where people abandon all hope before entering Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.42,clover,,0,0,0,,Abandon all hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:39.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Doré that you like uses that theme, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:46.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Since they chose this motif, they must've been stressed about something as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:48.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Marble, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Seems like there's a dull light coming from the inside, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:05.16,clover,,0,0,0,,That's because the light is being refracted inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:08.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Marble is actually translucent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.36,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:20.70,clover,,0,0,0,,H-Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.49,clover,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.76,clover,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:32.47,thoughts,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.12,thoughts,,0,0,0,,He has his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.79,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:47.38,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right to take that away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:54.44,clover,,0,0,0,,No way, you f-finally got a call from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:54.44,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,345)\fad(488,0)}Waha, it's been a while, Mayama-san
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.27,clover,,0,0,0,,From Spain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:57.45,clover,,0,0,0,,From Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:00.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:04.22,clover,,0,0,0,,The Spanish architect, Marc Carlos?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:08.45,clover,,0,0,0,,He's on the project with Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.58,clover,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:13.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Man, she's really in a bind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:17.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seriously... I can figure out the situation just from this picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:23.16,clover,,0,0,0,,It seems like he's totally in love with Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika, Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:30.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika, Rika, Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:30.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:37.87,clover,,0,0,0,,He's Spain's top runner after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.54,clover,,0,0,0,,He must come on strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.28,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Rika-san is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:46.33,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't she worn down enough already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.84,clover,,0,0,0,,So she faxed Mayama an SOS...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.04,clover,,0,0,0,,She's gonna use him as a guard dog, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Please say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:10:01.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, as long as I'm with her, I won't let anyone lay a finger on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:15.31,dog,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(350,71)}Miwako-san!!!\NI smell a beast in this man!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:10.44,clover,,0,0,0,,No! He's probably the most dangerous person by Rika's side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Instead of a guard dog, he's already turned into a rabid dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.31,clover,,0,0,0,,A wolf on the outside and a rabid dog on the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.65,clover,,0,0,0,,It must've been a tough choice, after putting those two on the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.41,clover,,0,0,0,,How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:28.88,clover,,0,0,0,,But doesn't Rika-san look even thinner in this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:33.24,clover,,0,0,0,,If I could, I'd fly there myself and take her under my wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm already prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.09,clover,,0,0,0,,A miniature rice cooker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:40.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Along with a voltage converter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:48.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Even when she's not hungry, she can eat rice with bonito flakes and soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.88,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Miso and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:51.86,clover,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Pickled seaweed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.72,clover,,0,0,0,,It's like a care package from home...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Somen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.61,clover,,0,0,0,,But somen is pretty good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Do they have seasoning for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:06.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Somen is flavorless without beefsteak and green onion...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't they have ginger over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.09,clover,,0,0,0,,They should have plenty of herbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:12.87,clover,,0,0,0,,...like mint and lemon baim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:18.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Please! Mint and lemon balm on somen?! That's not fit for human consumption!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:22.05,clover,,0,0,0,,That's on the same level as Yamada's special menus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.80,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:24.80,clover,,0,0,0,,B-B-Behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:28.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Not cow. I'm talking about somen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:28.03,note,,0,0,0,,[ In Japanese, "ushiro" means "behind" and "ushi" means "cow". ]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:30.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Either way, I can't let Rika-san eat something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.34,clover,,0,0,0,,I... can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:37.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Daikon sprouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:43.91,clover,,0,0,0,,Daikon sprouts are spicy, so they're great as spice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:48.63,clover,,0,0,0,,You can eat them after three days if you spread them on top of a damp cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:52.79,clover,,0,0,0,,You should take some seeds and plant them as soon as you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:57.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.32,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll try that as soon as I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.83,clover,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:29.40,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.60,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'll try that as soon as I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:33.96,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.64,clover,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.29,clover,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:47.09,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,385)\fad(441,0)}Yamada-san, wait up, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:50.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.35,clover,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:10.64,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm taking Leader for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.33,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:16.33,clover,,0,0,0,,You really wanted me to come chasing after you, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.38,clover,,0,0,0,,N-No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Of course not! I really didn't think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.12,clover,,0,0,0,,P-Please don't stare at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:41.44,clover,,0,0,0,,You said it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:43.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:12.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:17.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Won't you please talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:29.07,clover,,0,0,0,,You can see what Hagu is up against, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:35.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Your paths will separate if you don't talk to her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:37.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.27,clover,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:45.04,clover,,0,0,0,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:47.49,clover,,0,0,0,,"It can't be helped"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, split or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.24,clover,,0,0,0,,...we were never that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.00,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.93,clover,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:04.84,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}umaku hanashi ga dekinakute\NI feel really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:09.40,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hontou wa sumanai to omotteru\N...that I can't say it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:14.50,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}shibaraku nayandemo mitakedo\NI worried over it for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.83,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:19.46,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sono uchi tsukarete nemutteru\N...but I eventually gave up and fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.46,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:24.35,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}shuumatsu no kono machi no kuuki wa\NThe air in this town on the weekend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:29.42,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitoikire de musekaeri\N...is heavy with the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:34.34,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fukaku tameiki wo tsuitara\NWhen I let out a deep sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:38.77,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}gaitou speaker ni kesareta\N...the external speaker overrode it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.79,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.04\fay0.005\fad(1250,935)\fnCambria\fs36\pos(376,123)\frz359.089\frx358\fry16\c&H234854&\3c&H5B8EA6&\4a&H80&\bord1.25}Morita Technology Research Office
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:47.67,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sorerashii kotoba wo narabetemo\NEven when I try to say it well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:57.11,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsutawaru koto nado hajime kara nai\N...there never was anything to be communicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:04.81,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nigiyaka na kono machi no\NIn this busy town...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.20,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I always thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:16.90,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sora ni omoikiri hariageta koe wa\N...I look toward the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:08.41,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I always thought that there must be something that only I am capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.18,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wanted to think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.44,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:22.03,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}boku ni yasashiku shite kureta\NAnd to that person who was so kind to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.18,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll get Dad's company back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:29.02,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ano hito e no happy birthday\N...I shout out, "Happy birthday."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.67,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hey, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:36.54,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.93,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It heads toward the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:43.98,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It follows wherever the light leads it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.27,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:51.45,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nanika chiisana trouble de\NA slight trouble got us lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:56.26,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitodakari ni nomikomare\N...amongst the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:17:01.19,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dareka no tsumaranai joke ni\NAnd I started laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:06.09,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}honno sukoshi dake waratta\N...at people's stupid jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:10.81,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}itsuka kono machi no dokoka de\NI still don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:15.73,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi to guuzen deattemo\N...what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:20.74,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nani wo hanashitara ii no ka\N...if I were to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:25.38,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ima demo yoku wakaranai\N...randomly somewhere in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:35.04,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitotsu zutsu kowarete yuku sekai de\NWhat's the meaning behind the tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:43.82,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nagashita namida ni nan no imi ga aru\N...that I shed in this gradually crumbling world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:40.55,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,375)\fad(440,0)}We're not going for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:54.04,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nigiyaka na kono machi no sora ni\NIn this busy town...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:18:03.44,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}omoikiri hariageta koe wa\N...I look toward the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:08.66,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dokoka tooku no machi ni iru\NAnd to that person in a distant town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:15.34,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ano hito e no happy birthday\N...I shout out, "Happy birthday."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:26.97,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mayama-san is in Spain already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.67,clover,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.67,clover,,0,0,0,,You got your license, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, it's limited to an automatic though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Then, do you wanna go for a drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.52,clover,,0,0,0,,A drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:46.21,clover,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I've never driven outside the driving school without an instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:48.34,clover,,0,0,0,,I also don't have a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.79,clover,,0,0,0,,But we do have a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.02,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:58.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-You want to take my car out for an untried driver's first drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.34,clover,,0,0,0,,What kind of a penalty game is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:02.22,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right, the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.61,clover,,0,0,0,,The ocean, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.73,clover,,0,0,0,,The ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:08.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:09.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:13.64,clover,,0,0,0,,A normal car can only seat five people though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:20.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Me, Hagu-chan, Takemoto-kun, Morita-san, Sensei, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.36,clover,,0,0,0,,So one person won't fit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:28.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Mayama is in Spain now, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.58,clover,,0,0,0,,A five seater is okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:35.04,clover,,0,0,0,,We can wait until he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.59,clover,,0,0,0,,He said he'd be back in about a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:42.07,clover,,0,0,0,,It'll be less crowded and better once it's a little colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.55,clover,,0,0,0,,There'll be a bunch of seashells to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.63,clover,,0,0,0,,I want to pick up seashells!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:52.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, we've never gone to the beach together, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:56.88,clover,,0,0,0,,That's true, now that you mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:01.61,clover,,0,0,0,,We've taken a boat tour and gone to the hot springs, but we've never gone to the beach together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.53,clover,,0,0,0,,That sounds good. The ocean, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:09.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:28.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's all pack bentos, bring our cameras, take a lot of pictures, and eat a lot of food...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:34.45,clover,,0,0,0,,And pick up a lot of shells...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:38.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.33,clover,,0,0,0,,I bet it'll be a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:45.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:50.68,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:56.45,thoughts,,0,0,0,,In the end, we never went to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,For some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:04.65,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Even though we didn't have a single picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:10.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That image of everyone together burned into the back of our eyelids...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:17.46,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...became the one image that will stay with us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:29.84,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:29.84,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:40.30,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:40.30,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:43.72,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:43.72,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:52.85,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:52.85,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:22:06.33,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:22:06.33,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:09.07,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:09.07,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.93,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.93,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:16.27,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:16.27,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:24.97,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:24.97,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:28.37,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:28.37,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Forward, in the direction of the light.
